{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.720", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Befristungen sind f\u00fcr Besch\u00e4ftigte ein gro\u00dfes Problem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt Kettenbefristungen mit Sachgrund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die sind nicht akzeptabel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.000", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr brauchen wir eine zeitliche Begrenzung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.320", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber das weitaus gr\u00f6\u00dfere Problem ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.600", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Betriebe einfach so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne Grund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "befristen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb sind Befristungen ja auch kein Normalarbeitsverh\u00e4ltnis; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie sind prek\u00e4re Besch\u00e4ftigung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau deshalb wollen wir Gr\u00fcne sachgrundlose Befristungen abschaffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.840", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt will auch die AfD mit einem Gesetzentwurf angeblich gegen Befristungen vorgehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die sachgrundlose Befristung will sie aber nicht abschaffen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Gegenteil! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie will stattdessen die Befristungen mit Sachgrund aus dem Gesetz streichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.760", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das geht gar nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.400", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf diese Idee kommt ja nicht mal die FDP. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Befristungen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zwei Jahre lang, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne Grund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.720", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einfach so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.880", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "willk\u00fcrlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden dann zur Regel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.160", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Besch\u00e4ftigten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.440", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das sind ja in gro\u00dfer Zahl junge Menschen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.200", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "leben dann weiterhin in Unsicherheit und k\u00f6nnen ihre Zukunft nicht planen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.440", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran \u00e4ndert der Gesetzentwurf der AfD rein gar nichts."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.200", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt l\u00e4uft das bei der AfD alles unter dem Deckm\u00e4ntelchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.040", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man wolle Kettenbefristungen abschaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.280", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die vorgeschlagenen Regelungen w\u00e4ren aber nur f\u00fcr Unternehmen gut; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.360", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten h\u00e4tten sie verheerende Auswirkungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn dieser Gesetzentwurf zementiert sachgrundlose Befristungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nichts anderes als ein Angriff auf das Normalarbeitsverh\u00e4ltnis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist nicht akzeptabel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.720", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es kommt noch schlimmer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bisher ist ja eine erneute sachgrundlose Befristung im selben Betrieb nicht m\u00f6glich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.760", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD will aber eine Karenzzeit von drei Jahren einf\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.760", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danach k\u00f6nnte dieselbe Person im selben Betrieb wieder sachgrundlos befristet angestellt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade Gro\u00dfunternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.280", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bekanntlich am h\u00e4ufigsten befristen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.480", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel die Deutsche Post\u00a0AG, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden sich dar\u00fcber extrem freuen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn so k\u00f6nnen Besch\u00e4ftigte jahrelang und sogar dauerhaft in einem Konzern mit seinen Tochtergesellschaften hin- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.440", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und hergeschoben werden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach Lust und Laune, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "willk\u00fcrlich befristet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.320", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das dann auch noch rechtssicher. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.440", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau so entstehen Kettenvertr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.840", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.280", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit diesem Gesetzentwurf eigentlich verhindern wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist einfach nur absurd."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.520", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ich beantworte keine Frage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben heute schon gen\u00fcgend von Ihnen geh\u00f6rt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.000", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.400", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die von Befristungen betroffen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "helfen Ihre Ideen keinen Schritt weiter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.480", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen zeigt dieser Gesetzentwurf wirklich wundersch\u00f6n, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.880", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie gespalten die AfD ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.200", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch vor zwei Monaten hie\u00df es hier in diesem Plenum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.240", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie w\u00fcrden uns einen Gesetzentwurf mit Hand und Fu\u00df pr\u00e4sentieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.840", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damals dachte die AfD \u00fcber eine zeitliche H\u00f6chstgrenze f\u00fcr Befristungen nach, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenso \u00fcber eine h\u00f6here Zahlung der Arbeitgeber in die Arbeitslosenversicherung und \u00fcber eine Abfindungszahlung f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von all dem ist heute nichts mehr zu h\u00f6ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.800", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zeigt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.920", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie geben sich gerne sozial, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "tats\u00e4chlich sind Sie aber im Kern neoliberal."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Fazit: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.640", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Gesetzentwurf ist keine Alternative\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.600", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er ist einfach nur schlecht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.360", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn so entsteht noch mehr prek\u00e4re Besch\u00e4ftigung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.520", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir bleiben dabei: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die sachgrundlose Befristung ist nicht notwendig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.800", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie ist auch nicht fair. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.840", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb muss sie abgeschafft werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.080", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn die Menschen brauchen soziale Sicherheit und Perspektiven."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.000", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kollege Torbj\u00f6rn Kartes hat das Wort f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}